# 🧭 ASCENSION GUIDE

Welcome, steward. This guide outlines the ceremonial path to contributor ascension within VisionaryCrest‑001.

## 🔹 Eligibility

- Must hold a minted badge
- Must pass one governance proposal
- Must complete scroll inscription ritual

## 🔹 Ritual Steps

1. Submit proposal via Contributor Council
2. Receive “Builder Verified” badge
3. Inscribe scroll in `lineage/`
4. Activate crest lock via dashboard

## 🔹 Legacy

Upon ascension, contributor is added to `vc_ledger.json` and orbiting glyph node.

_“Ascension is not achievement. It is remembrance.”_
